query: 如图,四边形ABCD是矩形,点E和点F是矩形ABCD外两点,AE⊥CF于点H,AD=3,DC=4,DE=\frac{5}{2},∠EDF=90°,则DF长是()选项：['\\frac{15}{8}', '\\frac{11}{3}', '\\frac{10}{3}', '\\frac{16}{5}']
answer: 解:设DF和AE相交于O点,∵四边形ABCD是矩形,∴∠ADC=90°,∵∠EDF=90°,∴∠ADC+∠FDA=∠EDF+∠FDA,即∠FDC=∠ADE,∵AE⊥CF于点H,∴∠F+∠FOH=90°,∵∠E+∠EOD=90°,∠FOH=∠EOD,∴∠F=∠E,∴△ADE∽△CDF,∴AD:CD=DE:DF,∵AD=3,DC=4,DE=\frac{5}{2},∴DF=\frac{10}{3}．故选:C．
